%section#hero.hero-big.text-light.parallax-section{"data-parallax-image" => image_path('malls-balls-alt.jpg')}
  #page-title.wrapper-small.align-center
    = image_tag 'logo-large-white.png', style: 'width: 50%'
    %h6.title-alt.uppercase Investment Fund

%section#page-body
  .spacer-big
  .wrapper-small
    %h2 Entrepreneurship for fun and profit.
    .column-section.clearfix
      .column.one-half
        %p We're an early-stage investment fund based in Adelaide, Australia. We love startup companies that have potential to grow big, fast - solving problems, building jobs, and making money.
      .column.one-half.last-col
        %p We're technologists, CEOs, founders, marketers, lawyers and beer enthusiasts. We love entrepreneurship, and want to share what we've learned, and help others to win.

  .spacer-big
  .wrapper
    .column-section.clearfix
      .column.one-third.align-center
        %i.fa.fa-cubes.fa-5x
        %h3 Very early-stage investment
        %p Weâ€™re usually the first or second cheque, happy to lead or follow in a round. We invest up to $50k per round as a fund, but our members can (and do) invest on their own.
      .column.one-third.align-center
        %i.fa.fa-dollar.fa-5x
        %h3 We like to help, but not hold the reigns
        %p We're passionate about startups, and love to help with mentoring, introductions and technical advice where we can. But we also want to let entrepreneurs do what they do best.
      .column.one-third.last-col.align-center
        %i.ion.ion-heart.ion-6x
        %h3 With a focus on simplicity
        %p We pride ourselves on presenting terms you can understand without going to a lawyer (but you should still totally get a lawyer). We're nice people, too.
    .spacer-big
    .spacer-medium

    .wrapper-small.align-center
      %h6.title-alt.uppercase Think that you might be a good fit?
      %h2 Tell us why we should invest in you.
      .spacer-medium
      %p
        = link_to 'Apply', new_application_path, class: 'sr-button button-big'
    .spacer-big
